  Loop Manager                                  
  Trigger Queue                                 
                                                
› 1. Timer        Runs when timer-based loop    
                  triggers become due.          
  2. Idle         Runs after the main thread    
                  stays idle for the            
                  configured duration.          
  3. Before Turn  Runs before a user turn is    
                  submitted into the main       
                  thread model.                 
  4. After Turn   Runs after the assistant      
                  final response completes.     
                                                
